  "title": "HR and Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><em>Job Descriptions</em></p><ul><li>Assist to manage the full spectrum of HR and Admin  functions</li><li>Manage and handle employee’s records in iHRM System</li><li>Timely and accurate monthly payroll processing</li><li>Responsible for work pass administration</li><li>Assist to administer training related matters including coordination or enrolment of internal & external courses, update & maintain training record.</li><li>Ensure timely & accurate submissions in all government and related claims</li><li>Handle all employee inquiries on HR-related matters</li><li>Responsible for the timely, accurate and efficient preparation and management of documents</li><li>Undertake any ad-hoc projects assigned by the superior/management team from time to time</li></ul><p><em>Requirements</em></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma/ Degree with relevant experiences handling payroll</li><li>Minimum 3 years as Human Resource executive</li><li>Knowledge of labour regulations in Indochina region is preferred</li><li>A team player with a strong sense of responsibility & self-motivation to get tasks done independently</li><li>Able to start immediately or within a short notice</li></ul>",
